title: Thom Hartmann Program - January 16 2014
description:
January 16, 2014
The Thom Hartmann Program

Hour One: 4/20 friendly...burden or benefit to the economy?  Charles "Cully" Stimson, Heritage Foundation  / Plus, a Hunter School student shares her story

Hour Two: Isnt' it time for the WPA?  / Plus, Geeky Science - Your cat's tail and what it's telling you!

Hour Three: What does the right have against America's public schools?  Bob Bowdon, ChoiceMedia.tv
